channel.title: Does anyone here suffer from anxiety/panic attacks?
channel.description:
Hello I have been suffering from anxiety and panic attacks for close to 5 years now and its getting pretty bad now I was just wondering if anyone else here has the same thing and what you do to help yourself? I know they had medications to get the physical symptoms away but I have heard bad things about these and my parents don't want me taking it. If anyone here knows anything that will help I would appreciate it very much and if you want to share your story about your anxiety/panic attacks ill be happy to read them.
Thank-you for your time.
